data.description:
Welcome to your new home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this property provides the ideal backdrop for family living. On the main level you will find an open living area with kitchen, dining and living room. There is an oversized bedroom serving as the primary and an additional bedroom as well as a full bath. Downstairs you will find a basement area perfect for entertaining, relaxation, or accommodating guests, this space offers a world of possibilities. The third bedroom and laundry room completes the finished space. The one car garage is partially converted as well with very little work required to add an additional finished room. 
Step through to the rear of the house, and you'll find a covered porch and fenced back yard. This back covered patio and spacious back yard expand your living space, providing the perfect space for relaxation and entertainment. It's the ideal spot to create cherished memories with loved ones and enjoy the beauty of the outdoors right at your doorstep. Information gathered from Third Party and Tax Records and though assumed reliable, should be Verified by Buyer/Buyers Agent.
